/* Table: "MD_Entity2Company" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "MD_Entity2Company"
(
"Entity2CompID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"EntityID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"EntityCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"CompanyID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CompanyCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"StartTime" TIMESTAMP,
"EndTime" TIMESTAMP,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
constraint PK_MD_ENTITY2COMPANY primary key ("Entity2CompID")
);
